.DT
printerrors
Discworld creator help
printerrors

.SH Name
.SI 5
printerrors - write all bugreports in a series of directories.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
printerrors <directory>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will collect all error reports in <directory> and all
subdirectories of it, and write them to /w/<creator>/print_errors.txt
.EP
.SP 5 5
Since it's coded to be nice to the other players, it will take a while to
check all directories if there are a lot of them, and will tell you when
it's finished.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
printerrors /d/am    (this will take a long time:)
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
errors, finderrors
.EP
